|X|\geq c
\alpha=0.2
c
\dfrac{\alpha}{2}=1-\dfrac{c+3}{6},c=2.4
\beta=\dfrac{2.4+4}8-\dfrac{-2.4+4}8=0.6
W=\{{x: |x| \geq c}\}
\begin{align}\beta(\theta) &=P[|X| \geq c|\theta] \\ &=1-\frac{c}{\theta}\end{align}
=P[X\in W|\theta=3]=1-\frac{c}{3}
=P[X\in W'|\theta=4]=1-P[X\in W|\theta=4]=\frac{c}{4}
